{
  "stem": "24515.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the end, I managed to get him closer to where I was, and then I moved to where he was, and that's another very long story, [INAUDIBLE] one, but in the end we got together.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we can look up the date.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I-- I think that's my defense.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember dates.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know when my father died, my mother-- I just don't remember these things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But relatively soon after we left, after Kristallnacht, my father was prohibited any activity.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I managed, somehow-- that's another very long, and-- and very involved story, to get the English visa for my parents.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My parents kept [? bugging me about ?] buying this, buying that-- setting up what's called lifts in those days.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Enormous creates, you see, in which-- [INAUDIBLE] getting them ready.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, I was thinking why are you getting ready lifts for?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Come here already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, as I told you before, I don't think my father really wanted to come.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not only because of his German philosophy, but also because he knew perfectly well that a German lawyer had very little chance of making a living, let alone for his children, you know, in countries other than Germany.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what he did was, he hesitated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can show you the telegram.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A few days before war broke out, I wired them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, Paul was very ill-- I hoped they would realize, Paul was standing for politics, or something, or [INAUDIBLE]-- better you come immediately.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father wired back to the effect that I was to keep an eye open and so on, so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He hoped he wasn't quite that bad, but if necessary, he'd come alone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like hell, he'd come alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
